Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Candidates consider TV debate
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w4q8
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 14 Sep 1980
Three-way TV debate for presidential candidates could leave Carter at a disadvantage. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less